";
CM_ SG_ 1057 VehicleSpeedOverGroundEstCounter "Counter for VehicleEstSpeedOverGround.
";
CM_ SG_ 1024 VehicleConfParametersHS "Signal used for the distribution of Vehicle Configuration parameters.

See doc 31812330 'Car Configuration EuCD - Vehicle Configuration Parameters'.
";
CM_ SG_ 1029 VehicleInfoParametersHS "Contains signals for Network/Node management, diagnostic freeze frame info and Software sequrity request.

See doc 31812331 'Car Configuration EuCD - Vehicle Information Parameters'.
";
